        <abstract>
            <p>GP has been asked to recommend a naturalist to sail with Capt. Robert FitzRoy to Tierra del Fuego and the South Sea Islands. If Leonard Jenyns is not available, whom would JSH recommend?</p>
            <p>P.S. Urges JHS not to lose this opportunity to have collections made for "our museum".</p>
